  "text": "The radiation condition at infinity in medium 1 at z > 0 has the view: k z1 > 0 and in medium 2 at z < 0: k z2 > 0. It is necessary to say that (3) does not have any solution without loss at least in one of the considered media. The results of numerical calculation of characteristics equation (3) present in Figure 1 for the dependence of wave attenuation and phase velocity on the imaginary complex permittivity parts \u03b5 2 . The algorithm to define the roots of a complex equation described in [CITATION_1] .",
